schools.name: Crenshaw Science, Technology, Engineering, Math And Medicine Magnet

data.description: PRICED TO SELL!!!!! Welcome to this charming family home! First time on the market in over 58 years!!! Walk into a spacious, bright, open living room with a tray ceiling that flows directly into a large dining room through an elegant archway. Two great size bedrooms and a den. Nice kitchen with eat in dining area. Separate laundry room with washer and dry hook ups. Newer laminate flooring throught out. Freshly painted total interior.  Well manicured backyard for relaxing and entertaining. Bonus unit in the back offers a large open living room with an additional room that has been newly painted with new flooring. This area would be perfect for considering an ADU!!!! Detached garage currently being used for storage. Long driveway, good neighborhood, centrally located, close to transportation, LAX, shopping, dining, entertainment including So-Fi Stadium, Intuit Dome and the Forum, Downtown L.A. This is a wonderful opportunity.....
